{"tid":1570558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[核彈]我宣佈今次運動名稱為「玄水革命」","createTime":"2019-09-15T06:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T08:26:35.000Z","uid":292710,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e16abefdc4906ec66438d154f378e5d12779c1a4","tid":1570558,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"在古代文學中，玄水／青龍為水銀之代稱，於道家丹道文化有廣泛應用。<br />\n玄（黑）衣，流水＝簡稱「玄水」<br />\n為何不用陳云根之「流水革命」一詞？因為陳云根妄圖利用此詞移植佛教文化於中國文化中。西方媒體受陳云根誤導，故有此名。<br />\n為何不用戴耀廷之「如水革命」一詞？因為如水出自儒家之「君子之交淡如水，小人之交甘若醴。」<br />\n為何不用「若水／似水」革命？因為兩者皆是出自非原版之道德經，原版為治水。原版為「天道無親，恒與善人」而非通行本之「天道無親，常與善人。」<br />\n<br />\nTLDR：採用「玄水革命」最符合原始道家文化。"},{"pid":"6e015941f17c0ea28a65644a92f4edf1b5fcfdfe","tid":1570558,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mHO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=b233cf8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mHO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=878ce745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"de18c30360f5599bdf748372384ddcff8ea3097e","tid":1570558,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁<br />\n[重要] 見到藍絲要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b680d867a85759a7e5cf54201663f75a3d44a3c5","tid":1570558,"uid":11798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"廢文 不推文上一頁"},{"pid":"ec1342ececca3c8d6c38884c72080e554